1
00:00:06,060 --> 00:00:08,340
♪The white sail came too late♪

2
00:00:09,100 --> 00:00:11,340
♪Where did he go?♪

3
00:00:12,340 --> 00:00:13,820
♪Snow veils the mountains♪

4
00:00:14,060 --> 00:00:16,340
♪Love endures beyond life and death♪

5
00:00:17,860 --> 00:00:19,580
♪A black chess piece♪

6
00:00:19,660 --> 00:00:23,140
♪Whose game did he stumble into?♪

7
00:00:23,740 --> 00:00:27,620
♪All his life, there's no escape♪

8
00:00:29,420 --> 00:00:33,340
♪In ten thousand years, what will still remain?♪

9
00:00:34,300 --> 00:00:40,020
♪Will anyone still love with an unchanging heart?♪

10
00:00:40,300 --> 00:00:42,620
♪I will remember♪

11
00:00:42,780 --> 00:00:46,660
♪Those days long past♪

12
00:00:47,660 --> 00:00:51,580
♪As the wind drifts with the white sail♪

13
00:00:52,220 --> 00:00:53,660
♪Ten thousand years ago♪

14
00:00:53,780 --> 00:00:57,500
♪Did you once walk this shore?♪

15
00:00:57,740 --> 00:01:02,940
♪Why can't our bond be severed in this life?♪

16
00:01:03,420 --> 00:01:05,100
♪I am lost yet willing♪

17
00:01:05,180 --> 00:01:09,580
♪Still I love you with a steadfast heart♪

18
00:01:12,140 --> 00:01:17,100
♪Until all things fade away♪

19
00:01:23,940 --> 00:01:27,220
♪The stars will remember us♪

20
00:01:27,220 --> 00:01:28,220
[Love & Crown]

21
00:01:28,220 --> 00:01:29,980
[Adapted from the novel "My Queen" by Xie Lounan]

22
00:01:29,980 --> 00:01:32,980
[Episode 21]

23
00:01:53,510 --> 00:01:54,900
I didn't expect Xiao Huan

24
00:01:55,070 --> 00:01:56,540
to be such a romantic.

25
00:01:57,110 --> 00:01:57,980
Don't move.

26
00:01:59,840 --> 00:02:00,980
How could this happen?

27
00:02:01,430 --> 00:02:02,490
Sorry to disappoint you.

28
00:02:02,510 --> 00:02:03,660
I've woken up.

29
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:24,410
This can't be!

30
00:02:25,310 --> 00:02:27,610
How could my Illusion-Butterfly Powder fail?

31
00:02:28,750 --> 00:02:31,500
How is it that you're both standing here?

32
00:02:34,870 --> 00:02:36,450
The Frost Reed can cure any poison.

33
00:02:37,030 --> 00:02:37,730
It seems

34
00:02:38,080 --> 00:02:39,610
your investigation wasn't thorough enough.

35
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:49,340
Cangcang!

36
00:02:49,750 --> 00:02:50,540
Zhong Lin!

37
00:02:50,750 --> 00:02:51,570
Are you all right?
We're fine.

38
00:02:52,470 --> 00:02:54,060
Thanks to the Puppet Incense that Xiao Qianqing brought,

39
00:02:54,080 --> 00:02:55,340
we managed to control one of the servants.

40
00:02:55,360 --> 00:02:55,980
Good.

41
00:02:56,280 --> 00:02:57,170
The antidote. Quickly.

42
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:03,010
Let's go.

43
00:03:12,800 --> 00:03:13,730
Release the branch leader.

44
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:15,060
And we'll leave you both with intact bodies!

45
00:03:15,470 --> 00:03:16,570
Clear the way.

46
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:18,540
Make way.

47
00:03:19,750 --> 00:03:20,540
Hurry!

48
00:03:59,400 --> 00:04:00,170
Xiao Huan,

49
00:04:00,310 --> 00:04:01,780
do you really think you can escape?

50
00:04:02,590 --> 00:04:04,170
I'll give you one more chance.

51
00:04:04,470 --> 00:04:06,570
Hand over the Moon-Eclipse,

52
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:09,570
or I'll make sure all of you lose your senses

53
00:04:09,800 --> 00:04:11,380
and perish with your meridians severed.

54
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:16,540
Zhong Lin.

55
00:04:19,430 --> 00:04:20,170
Insolent.

56
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:26,020
Protector, have mercy!

57
00:04:26,360 --> 00:04:27,540
I only sought to present

58
00:04:27,750 --> 00:04:29,290
the Moon-Eclipse to you.

59
00:04:29,480 --> 00:04:30,250
Is that so?

60
00:04:30,850 --> 00:04:31,970
My sources tell me you intend

61
00:04:32,560 --> 00:04:34,490
to become the Ghost King yourself.

62
00:04:54,630 --> 00:04:55,580
Die!

63
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:14,700
Luo Xianxue?

64
00:06:08,750 --> 00:06:09,730
Luo.

65
00:06:39,040 --> 00:06:40,170
I'm glad you're safe.

66
00:06:42,800 --> 00:06:43,580
That day,

67
00:06:44,120 --> 00:06:45,900
I watched you be engulfed in flames with my own eyes.

68
00:06:46,360 --> 00:06:48,340
Father sent someone to retrieve your body,

69
00:06:49,040 --> 00:06:50,540
and they found a severed finger on it as well.

70
00:06:50,950 --> 00:06:51,730
I thought

71
00:06:51,750 --> 00:06:53,220
I'd never see you again.

72
00:06:53,310 --> 00:06:55,020
How did you escape?

73
00:06:55,390 --> 00:06:57,100
There was a cellar in the liquor storage.

74
00:06:58,070 --> 00:06:59,020
I hid there

75
00:06:59,560 --> 00:07:01,730
and barely survived.

76
00:07:03,480 --> 00:07:04,250
You never came

77
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:07,170
looking for me.

78
00:07:09,870 --> 00:07:10,540
I knew

79
00:07:11,560 --> 00:07:13,370
His Majesty saw me as a thorn in his side.

80
00:07:13,720 --> 00:07:15,220
If I appeared recklessly,

81
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:17,490
I'd only bring you trouble.

82
00:07:18,360 --> 00:07:19,140
So,

83
00:07:19,870 --> 00:07:20,780
I planned

84
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:22,100
to wander the world.

85
00:07:24,720 --> 00:07:26,290
And now you've appeared out of nowhere.

86
00:07:27,830 --> 00:07:29,340
Do you intend to assassinate him?

87
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:32,810
Why?

88
00:07:36,310 --> 00:07:37,370
I don't want

89
00:07:39,190 --> 00:07:40,460
to see you hurt,

90
00:07:41,720 --> 00:07:42,490
suffering,

91
00:07:43,870 --> 00:07:44,930
or endangered because of him.

92
00:07:46,750 --> 00:07:47,540
Cangcang,

93
00:07:48,310 --> 00:07:49,540
he's your tribulation.

94
00:07:50,480 --> 00:07:52,020
Don't let yourself get entangled with him anymore.

95
00:07:53,830 --> 00:07:55,340
If you can't make up your mind,

96
00:07:55,720 --> 00:07:56,610
I can help.

97
00:08:00,560 --> 00:08:01,340
Luo,

98
00:08:02,040 --> 00:08:03,460
so much has happened

99
00:08:03,630 --> 00:08:05,460
between him and me since you left.

100
00:08:06,480 --> 00:08:07,540
It's not

101
00:08:07,950 --> 00:08:09,540
as simple as you think.

102
00:08:10,070 --> 00:08:11,780
Even I didn't expect some things.

103
00:08:14,190 --> 00:08:15,020
He and I...

104
00:08:17,830 --> 00:08:19,730
Nobody can decide our matters for me.

105
00:08:22,240 --> 00:08:23,580
I overstepped.

106
00:08:24,870 --> 00:08:26,220
That's not what I meant.

107
00:08:26,510 --> 00:08:27,610
Luo, I...

108
00:08:27,630 --> 00:08:28,290
Cangcang.

109
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:29,610
Have you forgotten?

110
00:08:30,950 --> 00:08:32,250
You saved my life.

111
00:08:32,870 --> 00:08:33,850
Protecting you

112
00:08:34,320 --> 00:08:35,820
is my lifelong duty.

113
00:08:37,480 --> 00:08:39,250
I don't want to see you harmed in any way.

114
00:08:43,030 --> 00:08:45,610
I heard they raided an evildoer's base around here.

115
00:08:45,720 --> 00:08:47,460
Many missing children were found.

116
00:08:47,840 --> 00:08:50,420
Many of them were silenced.

117
00:08:54,550 --> 00:08:55,340
He moved!

118
00:09:11,790 --> 00:09:12,610
They say

119
00:09:12,630 --> 00:09:13,730
you're dying.

120
00:09:15,090 --> 00:09:15,860
I won't allow it.
Luo Xianxue,

121
00:09:16,690 --> 00:09:17,760
you are not to die

122
00:09:17,760 --> 00:09:18,710
without my permission.

123
00:09:22,030 --> 00:09:27,010
I, Luo Xianxue, swear to the heavens.

124
00:09:27,030 --> 00:09:30,530
From now on, I belong to Ling Cangcang.

125
00:09:30,550 --> 00:09:31,770
No matter how hard it gets,

126
00:09:31,790 --> 00:09:33,180
I will stay strong

127
00:09:33,240 --> 00:09:34,770
for Ling Cangcang.

128
00:09:34,790 --> 00:09:36,010
No matter how hard it gets,

129
00:09:36,030 --> 00:09:37,340
I will stay strong

130
00:09:37,480 --> 00:09:38,940
for Ling Cangcang.

131
00:09:40,550 --> 00:09:41,340
Cangcang,

132
00:09:42,120 --> 00:09:43,130
it's for you

133
00:09:43,790 --> 00:09:46,460
that I crawled my way out of that fire.

134
00:09:51,360 --> 00:09:52,180
Luo,

135
00:09:53,550 --> 00:09:54,940
ever since you joined the Ling family,

136
00:09:55,270 --> 00:09:57,340
you've always been a brother to me.

137
00:09:57,870 --> 00:09:58,850
Do you remember

138
00:09:59,030 --> 00:10:01,580
the vow I made when I entered the palace?

139
00:10:01,790 --> 00:10:03,980
I will protect everyone in the Ling family.

140
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:05,420
I've never changed.

141
00:10:06,550 --> 00:10:07,340
It's just...

142
00:10:10,270 --> 00:10:11,530
With Xiao Huan,

143
00:10:12,790 --> 00:10:13,530
I now...
So,

144
00:10:15,030 --> 00:10:16,370
no matter how much he hurts you,

145
00:10:17,630 --> 00:10:18,940
you won't hurt him back.

146
00:10:19,630 --> 00:10:20,420
Is that right?

147
00:10:27,320 --> 00:10:28,060
Luo,

148
00:10:28,720 --> 00:10:29,770
I think there are many misunderstandings

149
00:10:29,840 --> 00:10:31,130
between you two.

150
00:10:31,840 --> 00:10:33,650
It will take time to clear them up.

151
00:10:34,750 --> 00:10:35,460
All right.

152
00:10:36,390 --> 00:10:37,490
If that's the case,

153
00:10:38,390 --> 00:10:39,460
we'll talk next time.

154
00:10:41,790 --> 00:10:42,580
Good.

155
00:10:50,960 --> 00:10:51,530
Cangcang,

156
00:10:52,510 --> 00:10:53,730
I remember you've always loved

157
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:55,220
pear blossom honey since you were little.

158
00:10:56,000 --> 00:10:56,770
I brought some

159
00:10:57,600 --> 00:10:58,650
especially for you.

160
00:10:59,630 --> 00:11:00,490
I didn't expect

161
00:11:01,030 --> 00:11:02,650
you still remember after all this time.

162
00:11:03,270 --> 00:11:04,100
Of course.

163
00:11:19,030 --> 00:11:19,980
Try it while it's warm.

164
00:11:35,080 --> 00:11:36,300
It's the taste I remember.

165
00:12:11,790 --> 00:12:12,770
It's been...

166
00:12:15,550 --> 00:12:16,460
It's been...

167
00:12:18,480 --> 00:12:19,100
Cangcang!

168
00:13:18,720 --> 00:13:19,490
Luo Xianxue.

169
00:13:20,600 --> 00:13:21,980
I know why you came.

170
00:13:22,790 --> 00:13:24,580
If you really wanted to be dead,

171
00:13:25,000 --> 00:13:26,100
you wouldn't show up.

172
00:13:26,510 --> 00:13:27,770
Let's cut the chatter.

173
00:13:28,480 --> 00:13:29,700
Hand over the Moon-Eclipse

174
00:13:30,120 --> 00:13:31,490
and face your fate.

175
00:13:32,960 --> 00:13:34,530
Do you know what you're saying?

176
00:13:35,030 --> 00:13:36,010
There will be

177
00:13:36,630 --> 00:13:37,700
a battle between us.

178
00:13:39,000 --> 00:13:40,060
Have you thought about

179
00:13:40,550 --> 00:13:41,850
what will happen to Cangcang?

180
00:13:41,870 --> 00:13:42,890
I will never hurt her.

181
00:13:42,960 --> 00:13:44,460
You already have.

182
00:13:45,030 --> 00:13:46,460
You know Ling Xuefeng is using you

183
00:13:46,510 --> 00:13:47,530
to rebuild the Lingbi Sect,

184
00:13:47,790 --> 00:13:49,650
yet you willingly serve as his dog.

185
00:13:50,200 --> 00:13:52,100
You know how Cangcang feels about me,

186
00:13:52,550 --> 00:13:54,530
yet you help Ling Xuefeng to kill me.

187
00:13:55,120 --> 00:13:56,100
What do you expect

188
00:13:56,200 --> 00:13:57,370
Cangcang to think or do?

189
00:14:01,720 --> 00:14:02,850
Enough talk.

190
00:14:03,030 --> 00:14:03,850
Fight me!

191
00:14:05,600 --> 00:14:06,250
Stop!

192
00:14:12,360 --> 00:14:12,980
Cangcang...
You lied to me.

193
00:14:15,200 --> 00:14:16,250
You weren't supposed to be...

194
00:14:16,320 --> 00:14:18,300
I've used inner force to remove the sedative in the pear blossom honey.

195
00:14:19,270 --> 00:14:21,100
Your "death" was flawless.

196
00:14:22,360 --> 00:14:23,980
You couldn't have done it alone.

197
00:14:26,030 --> 00:14:27,490
What's really going on?

198
00:14:29,550 --> 00:14:30,300
Cangcang,

199
00:14:31,550 --> 00:14:32,940
you and Father

200
00:14:33,550 --> 00:14:34,770
saved my life.

201
00:14:35,320 --> 00:14:36,220
I must obey

202
00:14:37,150 --> 00:14:38,370
his command.

203
00:14:38,790 --> 00:14:39,530
My father?

204
00:14:41,510 --> 00:14:42,730
What order did my father give you?

205
00:14:44,270 --> 00:14:45,010
He must die

206
00:14:45,960 --> 00:14:47,010
today.

207
00:14:47,750 --> 00:14:48,610
You won't succeed!
Cangcang,

208
00:14:49,550 --> 00:14:50,340
move aside!

209
00:14:55,320 --> 00:14:57,250
The Xiaoxing Guards are already lying in wait.

210
00:14:57,750 --> 00:14:59,340
You can't do anything to me.

211
00:15:07,120 --> 00:15:07,980
Luo Xianxue,

212
00:15:09,240 --> 00:15:11,580
you loyally serve Grand Tutor Ling.

213
00:15:12,270 --> 00:15:13,300
But sadly,

214
00:15:14,360 --> 00:15:15,650
you're a fool.

215
00:15:16,120 --> 00:15:18,700
Do you know what Grand Tutor Ling has done?

216
00:15:20,480 --> 00:15:21,940
Whatever he does,

217
00:15:22,600 --> 00:15:23,820
it's all for the Ling clan

218
00:15:24,390 --> 00:15:25,300
and Cangcang.

219
00:15:25,790 --> 00:15:26,580
Is it?

220
00:15:27,270 --> 00:15:28,530
Do you know Grand Tutor Ling

221
00:15:28,550 --> 00:15:30,850
poisoned Ling Cangcang to force His Majesty

222
00:15:31,030 --> 00:15:33,100
to give her the cure?

223
00:15:36,120 --> 00:15:38,220
Were his actions really for Ling Cangcang's sake?

224
00:15:41,270 --> 00:15:42,010
What?

225
00:15:45,550 --> 00:15:46,490
My father...

226
00:15:52,510 --> 00:15:53,530
Was it

227
00:15:54,840 --> 00:15:55,850
the pear blossom honey?

228
00:15:56,320 --> 00:15:58,460
Grand Tutor Ling brought this pear blossom honey today.

229
00:15:58,510 --> 00:15:59,940
I added four spoonfuls as instructed.

230
00:15:59,940 --> 00:16:04,540
♪The rouge spilling into old snow...♪

231
00:16:06,550 --> 00:16:07,340
Luo Xianxue,

232
00:16:08,360 --> 00:16:09,580
surrender yourself.

233
00:16:09,750 --> 00:16:10,730
Never!
Wait.

234
00:16:12,500 --> 00:16:16,980
♪Oaths wither at the root of the tongue♪

235
00:16:18,140 --> 00:16:23,340
♪Only a wisp of smoke binds the butterfly...♪

236
00:16:24,320 --> 00:16:25,060
Your Majesty.

237
00:16:29,200 --> 00:16:29,980
Let him go.

238
00:16:31,550 --> 00:16:32,460
Let him go?

239
00:16:32,790 --> 00:16:33,530
Cangcang!
Go!

240
00:16:36,750 --> 00:16:38,180
I never want to see you again.

241
00:16:41,120 --> 00:16:41,890
Leave!

242
00:16:42,460 --> 00:16:45,460
♪And to share the red kiss of a blade upon the neck♪

243
00:16:45,620 --> 00:16:46,780
♪We brew our hottest tears...♪

244
00:16:47,960 --> 00:16:48,580
Very well.

245
00:16:50,030 --> 00:16:50,820
Leave.

246
00:16:56,820 --> 00:17:01,980
♪The cinnabar between my brows has turned to icy flakes♪

247
00:17:03,020 --> 00:17:05,300
♪The empty pouch you gave♪

248
00:17:05,380 --> 00:17:07,780
♪Is filled with my grief♪

249
00:17:10,140 --> 00:17:15,260
♪If yearning for each other is a tribulation♪

250
00:17:16,220 --> 00:17:21,020
♪I should've broken my sword and rejected the invitation♪

251
00:17:21,740 --> 00:17:23,940
♪So much for vows of growing old together...♪

252
00:17:25,200 --> 00:17:26,220
So it was all

253
00:17:27,880 --> 00:17:29,050
my father's doing...

254
00:17:30,550 --> 00:17:31,770
You should go back.

255
00:17:32,640 --> 00:17:34,050
I need some time to myself.

256
00:17:36,620 --> 00:17:38,020
♪Using the sweetest curse♪

257
00:17:38,180 --> 00:17:39,660
♪To build the coldest graveyard♪

258
00:17:39,780 --> 00:17:42,940
♪Buried under the parasol tree during the sorrowful night rain♪

259
00:17:43,060 --> 00:17:46,140
♪Are destined to meet on that autumn day of White Dew♪

260
00:17:46,460 --> 00:17:49,100
♪Shattering glazed fantasy with these sewn shoes♪

261
00:17:49,620 --> 00:17:50,900
♪Using the sweetest curse♪

262
00:17:51,220 --> 00:17:52,700
♪To build the coldest graveyard♪

263
00:17:52,860 --> 00:17:55,980
♪Buried under the parasol tree during the sorrowful night rain♪

264
00:17:56,100 --> 00:17:59,180
♪Are destined to meet on that autumn day of White Dew♪

265
00:17:59,500 --> 00:18:02,140
♪And to share the red kiss of a blade upon the neck...♪

266
00:18:02,790 --> 00:18:03,570
I wish

267
00:18:03,750 --> 00:18:05,010
to resign of my own accord.

268
00:18:06,200 --> 00:18:07,460
I only ask that Your Majesty

269
00:18:08,350 --> 00:18:09,660
will be merciful

270
00:18:10,030 --> 00:18:10,860
and spare

271
00:18:13,310 --> 00:18:14,700
my only daughter.

272
00:18:36,620 --> 00:18:39,860
[Qi]

273
00:19:25,880 --> 00:19:27,460
They've returned at last.

274
00:19:43,750 --> 00:19:47,490
We welcome the return of His Majesty and Her Majesty.

275
00:20:55,070 --> 00:20:56,810
It's been a while, everyone.

276
00:20:57,310 --> 00:20:58,620
I hope all has been well.

277
00:21:03,590 --> 00:21:04,980
I dare to ask,

278
00:21:05,640 --> 00:21:07,730
Your Highness, how much longer

279
00:21:08,640 --> 00:21:10,420
will you govern on behalf of His Majesty?

280
00:21:12,790 --> 00:21:13,730
Well...

281
00:21:14,880 --> 00:21:17,180
His Majesty's health has greatly improved

282
00:21:17,510 --> 00:21:19,250
but still requires rest.

283
00:21:19,640 --> 00:21:22,420
You'll have to deal with me for a while longer,

284
00:21:22,680 --> 00:21:23,940
Grand Tutor Ling.

285
00:21:24,480 --> 00:21:27,460
