574
00:39:29,510 --> 00:39:30,740
never stops.

575
00:39:31,680 --> 00:39:32,780
I believe

576
00:39:33,240 --> 00:39:35,340
this is the time to break the old ways

577
00:39:35,510 --> 00:39:37,220
and reform taxation.

578
00:39:38,320 --> 00:39:40,660
Prince of Yuzhang and I are of the same opinion.

579
00:39:41,110 --> 00:39:42,610
The current tax system

580
00:39:42,630 --> 00:39:43,930
has many types of levies

581
00:39:43,990 --> 00:39:45,820
which prompt frequent corruption by officials.

582
00:39:46,240 --> 00:39:47,300
I have also

583
00:39:47,760 --> 00:39:49,860
considered simplifying

584
00:39:49,880 --> 00:39:50,930
the collections

585
00:39:50,950 --> 00:39:52,090
and taxing by acreage instead.

586
00:39:52,470 --> 00:39:53,260
Of course,

587
00:39:53,550 --> 00:39:56,050
all this is still under discussion.

588
00:39:56,630 --> 00:39:58,740
If any minister has ideas,

589
00:39:58,760 --> 00:40:00,300
please present them to me.

590
00:40:08,680 --> 00:40:10,860
Since no one else has anything to say,

591
00:40:11,070 --> 00:40:11,930
we'll end

592
00:40:12,150 --> 00:40:13,380
today's session here.

593
00:40:34,240 --> 00:40:35,570
You're grinning without reason.

594
00:40:36,030 --> 00:40:37,860
What cunning scheme

595
00:40:38,320 --> 00:40:40,900
is your wise self plotting now?

596
00:40:41,430 --> 00:40:42,570
I just think

597
00:40:42,590 --> 00:40:45,010
you were especially impressive today.

598
00:40:45,320 --> 00:40:46,090
As a matter of fact,

599
00:40:46,590 --> 00:40:47,660
it has been a long time

600
00:40:47,800 --> 00:40:50,410
since we had a proper conversation.

601
00:40:50,800 --> 00:40:53,220
Feel free to enjoy this advantage you have earned.

602
00:40:54,680 --> 00:40:55,660
Well,

603
00:40:56,320 --> 00:40:57,610
what do you think of my idea?

604
00:40:57,920 --> 00:41:00,130
If the tax policies are simplified,

605
00:41:00,720 --> 00:41:02,380
officials will find it harder to cheat,

606
00:41:03,150 --> 00:41:05,820
so revenue should increase.

607
00:41:06,070 --> 00:41:07,300
More importantly,

608
00:41:07,760 --> 00:41:09,930
the people's tax burden will lessen.

609
00:41:10,510 --> 00:41:12,450
It is indeed a good proposal.

610
00:41:15,200 --> 00:41:16,220
However...

611
00:41:17,110 --> 00:41:17,900
However,

612
00:41:18,430 --> 00:41:19,410
the status verification issue

613
00:41:19,840 --> 00:41:21,090
only treats the symptoms, not the cause.

614
00:41:25,070 --> 00:41:26,010
We'll take it slow.

615
00:41:26,470 --> 00:41:27,410
Reform

616
00:41:27,590 --> 00:41:29,130
takes time.

617
00:41:37,590 --> 00:41:39,740
I heard you stopped Her Majesty's birth-control tea.

618
00:41:42,840 --> 00:41:43,970
You know about that?

619
00:41:45,070 --> 00:41:47,570
My mother cares about you having an heir

620
00:41:47,950 --> 00:41:49,340
much more than I do.

621
00:41:51,590 --> 00:41:52,450
I heard

622
00:41:53,200 --> 00:41:55,340
she is eager to find a princess consort for you.

623
00:41:55,880 --> 00:41:56,660
What do you say?

624
00:41:57,110 --> 00:41:59,700
Would you like me to find you a few?

625
00:42:00,150 --> 00:42:01,570
I do regret

626
00:42:01,840 --> 00:42:03,930
meddling and saving you.

627
00:42:14,880 --> 00:42:15,660
Look.

628
00:42:16,630 --> 00:42:17,530
Victory is mine.

629
00:42:25,990 --> 00:42:26,780
Your Majesty,

630
00:42:26,880 --> 00:42:28,970
is it true that you can roast pears?

631
00:42:29,360 --> 00:42:30,130
Yes.

632
00:42:31,240 --> 00:42:34,090
This is a recipe my mother invented.

633
00:42:40,280 --> 00:42:41,220
When I was little,

634
00:42:41,920 --> 00:42:43,010
I remember often

635
00:42:43,400 --> 00:42:44,820
roasting pears with my master

636
00:42:44,920 --> 00:42:45,900
and father...

637
00:42:47,240 --> 00:42:48,660
The Grand Tutor roasts pears too?

638
00:42:49,550 --> 00:42:50,780
I haven't roasted them

639
00:42:51,470 --> 00:42:52,970
in a while as well.

640
00:42:54,430 --> 00:42:55,010
Father.

641
00:42:55,030 --> 00:42:57,220
Greetings, Your Majesty.

642
00:42:59,760 --> 00:43:00,530
Please be seated.

643
00:43:01,880 --> 00:43:02,660
You as well, Your Majesty.

644
00:43:10,720 --> 00:43:11,860
Let me tell you something.

645
00:43:12,760 --> 00:43:13,860
Only the Jinye pears

646
00:43:14,430 --> 00:43:17,900
from Shuiquan Village are best for roasting.

647
00:43:18,550 --> 00:43:20,340
They are full of juice.

648
00:43:20,840 --> 00:43:21,930
Once they're grilled,

649
00:43:21,950 --> 00:43:23,180
spread some

650
00:43:23,800 --> 00:43:25,700
of your favourite pear blossom honey on them.

651
00:43:26,430 --> 00:43:27,490
You used to love it

652
00:43:27,630 --> 00:43:29,220
as a child.

653
00:43:54,580 --> 00:43:59,420
♪Who walks lone through storm and snow♪

654
00:44:00,180 --> 00:44:03,340
♪Reading every warmth and chill♪

655
00:44:04,300 --> 00:44:07,100
♪Of the heart?♪

656
00:44:09,060 --> 00:44:13,260
♪Who stands proud against a thousand weights♪

657
00:44:14,020 --> 00:44:17,460
♪Grace only a mask he wears?♪

658
00:44:17,700 --> 00:44:20,780
♪My blade sweeps the heavens♪

659
00:44:21,700 --> 00:44:24,220
♪Blood once drenched♪

660
00:44:24,980 --> 00:44:27,700
♪My armor and charging steed♪

661
00:44:28,380 --> 00:44:30,580
♪I know what it means to let go♪

662
00:44:31,500 --> 00:44:34,900
♪When to step in, when to hold back♪

663
00:44:35,340 --> 00:44:38,460
♪A broken blade cuts through♪

664
00:44:38,860 --> 00:44:41,620
♪Years of winter and summer♪

665
00:44:42,500 --> 00:44:44,540
♪Enemy flags burn to ash like gauze♪

666
00:44:45,380 --> 00:44:50,580
♪Yet my heart still bears the scars of rise and fall♪

667
00:44:50,740 --> 00:44:56,700
♪I'm willing to wield my sword with you and burn the waning moon♪

668
00:44:57,980 --> 00:45:03,860
♪I'm willing to brave all storms with you, boiling with passion♪

669
00:45:04,660 --> 00:45:10,820
♪I'm willing to break my wings and become the blade in your hand♪

670
00:45:11,620 --> 00:45:17,820
♪I'm willing to write with you this torn, enduring page of history♪

671
00:45:18,740 --> 00:45:24,540
♪I'm willing to travel thousands of miles, seeking your ambition♪

672
00:45:25,780 --> 00:45:31,740
♪I'm willing to give my life to keep you safe for a lifetime♪

673
00:45:32,580 --> 00:45:39,100
♪I'm willing to sing through every farewell and wait for you another thousand years♪

674
00:45:39,540 --> 00:45:46,980
♪I'm willing to live and die with you, my one and only wish in this lifetime♪

